caption.p: Determination the effects of SFJD on cell viability in RAW264.7 cells. (A) SFJD; (B) oseltamivir. RAW264.7 cells were infected with H1N1 at an MOI of 20 in the treatment of different doses of SFJD or oseltamivir for 24 h. Cytotoxicity of SFJD or oseltamivir to RAW264.7 cells was measured by MTT assays. Data are presented as mean Â± SD. The experiments were performed in triplicate.
